#wrapper
  h1
    img src=asset_url("Clock_alt.png") /
    | CommonTime
    sup a tool aimed to simplify finding common working hours for different timezones
  #main
    #myTime
      h2 Worker
      img default-src=asset_url("freelancer.png") src=asset_url("freelancer.png") /
      select.zoneSelector name="myTime" 
      input placeholder=("Enter email") type="email" /
    .chartWrap
      #chart
      #hoursFormatSelectorWrapper
        select name="am_pm_switch" 
          option selected="" value="24" 24 hours format
          option value="12" 12 hours format
    #clientTime
      h2 Client
      img default-src=asset_url("client.png") src=asset_url("client.png") /
      select.zoneSelector name="clientTime" 
      input placeholder=("Enter email") type="email" /
  footer
    #instruction.mb10
      h3 Instructions
      | To adjust freelancer's and client's working hours resize colored curves by dragging knobs (small circles) at their ends.
      | Email is used to load your gravatar.
      | Each activity i.e. updating emails, changing timezone or time format (12/24) will be immediately reflected in url.
      | The url then can be used to share current state of the timer to client and vice versa.
